	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Aegilops</i> <i>triuncialis</i> is dominant or co-dominant in the herbaceous layer. </div>
</div>

		
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text">  Herbs < 1 m; cover is intermittent to continuous. </div>
</div>

		
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Habitats</h4>
	<div class="text"> Upper slopes and outcrops on and off serpentine substrates. Soils are clayey.  </div>
</div>

		
